snippet.title: Dwarf Fortress on Steam Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/975370
Why is this coming to Steam FAQ: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Xwhi1KKp5QD9R4-euZ0JqRB0vHdNPqdBJXjIgp-yYHA/edit?usp=sharing

Soon it'll be easier than ever to play the legendary Dwarf Fortress. Coming to Steam, we have an all new trailer featuring never-before-seen graphics and audio.
